embeds.description:
New players are not able to build in the spawn town. If you would like to do so, you need to be verified. 

Verification is simple: 

1. Please read our [server rules](https://n3fs.co.uk/rules) and [guidelines](https://n3fs.co.uk/help/minecraft-guidelines).

2. Please post a message in <#258965196926746624>. Include your Minecraft username, and let us know you've read and agree to the rules.

That's it! One of the staff members will grant you access, usually within a few hours.
